        "URL": "data:text/html;charset=utf-8,%3C!doctype%20html%3E%0A%3Chtml%20lang%3D%22%22%3E%0A%3Chead%3E%0A%20%20%3Cmeta%20charset%3D%22utf-8%22%3E%0A%20%20%3Ctitle%3EPeep%20Surgery%3C%2Ftitle%3E%0A%3C%2Fhead%3E%0A%3Cbody%3E%0A%3Cbody%20text%3D%22%23000000%22%20link%3D%22%230000ff%22%20vlink%3D%22%23800080%22%20bgcolor%3D%22%23feff1f%22%3E%0A%0A%3Ccenter%3E%0A%3Ctable%20cellspacing%3D%220%22%20border%3D%220%22%20cellpadding%3D%227%22%20width%3D%22462%22%3E%0A%09%3Ctbody%3E%3Ctr%3E%0A%09%09%3Ctd%20width%3D%2223%25%22%20valign%3D%22TOP%22%3E%0A%09%09%09%3Ch1%20align%3D%22CENTER%22%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%2272%22%20height%3D%22112%22%3E%3C%2Fh1%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%0A%09%09%3Ctd%20width%3D%2255%25%22%20valign%3D%22MIDDLE%22%3E%0A%09%09%09%3Ch1%20align%3D%22CENTER%22%3EPeep%20Surgery%3C%2Fh1%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%0A%09%09%3Ctd%20width%3D%2222%25%22%20valign%3D%22TOP%22%3E%0A%09%09%09%3Ch1%20align%3D%22CENTER%22%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%2272%22%20height%3D%22112%22%3E%3C%2Fh1%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%0A%09%3C%2Ftr%3E%0A%3C%2Ftbody%3E%3C%2Ftable%3E%0A%3C%2Fcenter%3E%0A%0A%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EIntroduction%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%20One%20of%20the%20great%20mysteries%20of%20the%20Peep%20species%20is%20that%20these%20creatures%20are%20always%20born%20as%20conjoined%20quintuplets.%20%20Some%20scientists%20have%20theorized%20that%20this%20arrangement%2C%20much%20like%20pack%20behavior%20in%20other%20species%2C%20serves%20as%20a%20natural%20protection%20against%20predators.%20%20As%20evidence%2C%20note%20that%20Peeps%20are%20most%20often%20consumed%20by%20predators%20only%20after%20they%20have%20been%20separated%20from%20their%20siblings.%20%20Conversely%2C%20Peeps%20which%20remain%20attached%20to%20their%20siblings%20are%20rarely%20preyed%20upon.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%3Cp%3ENevertheless%2C%20as%20Peeps%20integrate%20into%20modern%20society%2C%20there%20is%20no%20ethical%20reason%20they%20should%20be%20denied%20the%20benefits%20of%20individualism%2C%20freed%20from%20the%20bonds%20of%20their%20sticky%2C%20marshmallow%20kin.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%3Cp%3EWe%20thus%20applied%20the%20advances%20of%20modern%20medicine%20to%20attempt%20this%20miracle%20separation%20of%20these%205%20brave%20volunteers.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%3Chr%3E%0A%0A%3Ccenter%3E%0A%3Ctable%20cellspacing%3D%220%22%20border%3D%220%22%20cellpadding%3D%227%22%20width%3D%22100%25%22%3E%0A%09%3Ctbody%3E%3Ctr%3E%0A%09%09%3Ctd%20valign%3D%22MIDDLE%22%3E%0A%09%09%09%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EMaterials%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%20In%20preparation%20of%20this%20never-before%20attempted%20surgery%2C%20a%20range%20of%20instruments%20and%20supplies%20were%20assembled.%20%20Our%20thanks%20go%20out%20to%20all%20those%20who%20will%20wonder%20on%20Monday%20where%20these%20instruments%20have%20gone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%0A%09%09%3Ctd%20width%3D%22386%22%20valign%3D%22MIDDLE%22%3E%0A%09%09%09%3Ccenter%3E%3Cimg%3E%3C%2Fcenter%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%0A%09%3C%2Ftr%3E%0A%3C%2Ftbody%3E%3C%2Ftable%3E%0A%3C%2Fcenter%3E%0A%0A%3Chr%3E%0A%0A%3Cb%3EProcedure%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%20%0A%0A%3Cul%3E%0A%09%3Cli%3E%3Cb%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%22surgery%2Fpart1.html%22%3EPhase%201%3A%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%20Pre-operative%20Peep%20patient%20preparation.%0A%09%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cb%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%22surgery%2Fpart2.html%22%3EPhase%202%3A%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%20Patients%20are%20transported%20to%20operating%20theater%2C%20where%20they%20are%20given%20anesthetic%20and%20surgery%20begins.%0A%09%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cb%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%22surgery%2Fpart3.html%22%3EPhase%203%3A%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%20After%20the%20first%20Peep%20is%20separated%2C%20wound%20is%20cauterized%20and%20first%20attempt%20at%20closure%20is%20carried%20out.%0A%09%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cb%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%22surgery%2Fpart4.html%22%3EPhase%204%3A%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%20The%20second%20Peep%20has%20been%20separated%2C%20and%20sutures%20are%20used%20to%20close%20the%20wound.%0A%09%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cb%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%22surgery%2Fpart5.html%22%3EPhase%205%3A%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%20Tension%20rises%20in%20the%20O.R.%20as%20a%20Code%20Purple%20is%20called.%0A%09%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cb%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%22surgery%2Fpart6.html%22%3EPhase%206%3A%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%20Reconstructive%20plastic%20surgery%20is%20carried%20out%20as%20the%20final%20step%20in%20this%20procedure.%0A%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%0A%0A%3Chr%3E%0A%0A%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20align%3D%22RIGHT%22%3E%3Cb%3E%3Ca%20name%3D%22results%22%3EOperative%3C%2Fa%3E%20Results%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%20Overall%2C%20we%20view%20this%20operation%20as%20a%20resounding%20success.%20%20All%20five%20patients%20survived%20the%20procedure%20as%20viable%2C%20if%20not%20somewhat%20squished%2C%20individuals.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%3Cp%3EFuture%20surgical%20technique%20should%20be%20refined%20based%20upon%20these%20experiences.%20%20We%20expect%20significant%20improvement%20in%20outcome%20with%20repeated%20attempts.%20%20Clearly%2C%20more%20data%20is%20required%20regarding%20base-line%20Peep%20vital%20signs%20and%20intraoperative%20monitoring.%20%20Established%20protocols%20for%20Code%20Purple%20resuscitation%20should%20be%20reviewed.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%22index.html%22%3EReturn%20to%20the%20Peep%20home%20page%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%0A%3C%2Fbody%3E%0A%3C%2Fbody%3E%0A%3C%2Fhtml%3E"
